==English==
===Etymology===
Derived from advertising for [[w:Absolut Vodka|Absolut Vodka]], which was in turn intended to capture the exotic sense of the brand's Swedish origin.

===Adjective===
'''absolut'''
# {{slang}}: [[absolute]], usually in reference to something represented as [[trendy]], [[popular]], or [[cutting-edge]].

